Commands for Raspberry Pi
IP address = 10.32.229.207
Command to start webcam streaming  = sudo mjpg_streamer -i "/usr/lib/input_uvc.so -d /dev/video0 -n -y f 15 -r 640x480" -o "/usr/lib/output_http.so -p 80 -w /usr/local/www"

Commands to start Motors
cd drv8835-motor-driver-rpi
sudo python example.py
this will start the example script which will run both motors forward and backwards once